transcript:
Customer: Hello
Customer: Hello
Executive: Hello
Customer: Hello Rahul ji.
Executive: Haan ji.
Executive: Sir hamari bhi baat sunenge keval apni baat bolenge.
Customer: Nahi nahi sunenge na aapki.
Executive: Haan sir sunenge main usi liye to main bol raha hu bas aap mere sath bas paanch minute ke liye video call pe aa jao sir main aapko link provide kar raha hu.
Executive: Theek hai hum bhi sir kuch aapko batayenge usme hamari bhi to baat samjhiye aap.
Customer: Nahi video call pe kaise aana hai sir main ye keh raha hu.
Executive: Sir main aapko ek google meet ka link send karunga jo hamari office ki mail id hai theek hai usse aapke mail pe main link send karunga theek hai usko join karenge.
Customer: Haan sir aawaz ji ji theek hai bhejiye aap haan aap phone se join karenge ya desktop se sir.
Executive: Haan aapke bhi aa rahi hai sir main apni screen share kar raha hu.
Customer: Phone se hi kar paunga.
Executive: Theek hai sir phone se join kariye.
Customer: Hmm.
Executive: Dekhiye sir fir screen dikh rahi hai sir aapko.
Customer: Hmm theek hai sir dikh rahi hai.
